      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS system has been addressed, ensuring precise variable valve timing, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers short, tactile throws paired with a firm clutch engagement. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. It sits on a well-damped suspension with refreshed bushings, providing the communicative feedback enthusiasts crave. While the finish shows light road-going patina, the drivetrain and limited-slip differential are dialed in for immediate performance.",
