      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2018 BMW 540i in Bluestone Metallic. This executive sedan offers a refined driving experience with its 335-hp turbocharged inline-six engine and smooth-shifting 8-speed automatic transmission. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though it shows minor, typical signs of road use, including a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim. The interior is a standout feature, finished in Mocha Dakota leather that remains supple and free of any punctures or unpleasant odors. All cabin technology, including the iDrive 6.0 navigation system, the Harman Kardon surround sound, and the multi-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is sound; it has been serviced at 10,000-mile intervals, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking luxury and performance without the new-car price tag. Service records are available for review.",
